OL,5, A care home has been closed after      
OL,6, inspectors discovered it was dirty and 
OL,7, understaffed, with a manager admitting 
OL,8, people's lives were at risk.           
OL,10,FTwo inspectors from the Care Quality   
OL,11,FCommission (CQC) arrived unannounced at
OL,12,FAshleigh House in Nottingham in May.   
OL,14,FThey found several problems at the     
OL,15,Fhome, which cared for 18 people with   
OL,16,Fautism and learning disabilities, and  
OL,17,Fplaced it in special measures.         
OL,19,FIt has now been closed by the provider 
OL,20,Fthat ran it, W Scott.                  
